{"tid":378734,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車路士同意3,500萬鎊簽張伯倫","createTime":"2017-08-28T16:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T08:09:18.000Z","uid":118114,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8aac436cb8b67df5b2fb156a502ab5fc67c9b9b0","tid":378734,"uid":118114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:55:55.000Z","msg":"車路士已簽認阿仙奴的開價，準備在周四轉會窗關閉前收購阿歷士張伯倫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/005543_da4a3be495199d681bb42e3a3e126199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F005543_da4a3be495199d681bb42e3a3e126199.jpg&h=abf66d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張伯倫將會跟車路士簽約5年，並準備在英格蘭集訓基地聖喬治公園進行體測。張伯倫是車路士今季第5簽。<br />\n<br />\n基昂：阿仙奴有大危機<br />\n<br />\n車路士對上兩場陣容都沒有英格蘭人，他們需要增強本地陣容。張伯倫的加盟亦令車路士可放走謝路美保加。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴曾向張伯倫開出新約，但被張伯倫拒絕，由於他的合約今季完結，所以雲格情願套現放他走。<br />\n<br />\n除了張伯倫外，李斯特城的真禾特都有機會在未來數天轉投車路士 。對上一名阿仙奴轉到車路士的球員為11年前的艾殊切高爾。"},{"pid":"edcf2dd0416fb8bb7f73c7d419509d5d979d0d1e","tid":378734,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:18:34.000Z","msg":"尋日仲幫阿記踢波, 今日就鬆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef121c835b1b2b0e0f19cd53183cfe7bcc16cdb","tid":378734,"uid":2772,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋日仲幫阿記踢波, 今日就鬆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯定係幫?"},{"pid":"c89fec713ed085a143a44c21c60c5ba3dabb8edf","tid":378734,"uid":60695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>尋日仲幫阿記踢波, 今日就鬆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯定係幫?</blockquote><br />\n&quot;同&quot;囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7f27d2b29294c59fd1f3c471b2f7c5c6eebd72","tid":378734,"uid":125432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s